-- Dombret Calls for Uniform Rules for State Debt, Boersen Reports
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2012-03-19T18:45:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-19/dombret-calls-for-uniform-rules-for-state-debt-boersen-reports.html
Bundesbank board member Andreas Dombret called for uniform rules regarding sovereign debt and
said collective action clauses should be included in the future
sale of government bonds,  Boersen-Zeitung  reported in a preview
of an article to be published tomorrow, citing an interview with
Dombret.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
